532
00:41:54.833 --> 00:41:56.583
Gravedigger stuff. I assume.

533
00:41:57.458 --> 00:41:59.708
He was the organist and the gravedigger?

534
00:42:00.208 --> 00:42:01.375
It's Kashubia.

535
00:42:25.208 --> 00:42:26.458
