693
00:53:49.416 --> 00:53:51.708
Filipiak? No. Him I knew.

694
00:53:56.916 --> 00:53:58.458
You know.

695
00:53:59.916 --> 00:54:01.666
I was transferred here as punishment

696
00:54:02.166 --> 00:54:05.083
